{"tid":999650,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［解夢J］我有可以隨便扭爆人地條頸嘅超能力","createTime":"2019-01-29T01:00:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-29T02:13:19.000Z","uid":149844,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"30041a2697d4fa5329cba8c40c23628ead2bc4fb","tid":999650,"uid":149844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T01:00:46.000Z","msg":"我係一個有超能力既人 <br />\n可以隨意扭斷人地個頭<br />\n係個荒無既地方（沙漠色）有個好似學校既地方<br />\n上緊堂既時候我同全班鬥力 弄斷曬全部人條頸<br />\n之後只剩少數同學同老師未死（仲反抗緊）<br />\n我掐死老師追喜愛的同學既頸 <br />\n之後係個個building 到同個老師玩追逐戰<br />\n之後嚇醒左<br />\n諗返都幾撚恐怖<br />\n有無大師識解下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f60b0f43a94953fe288892ca4752633f1b5893c","tid":999650,"uid":136186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T01:19:29.000Z","msg":"下世小心啲"},{"pid":"605804ff47622ffcf8381f2d56034a54ecdee4ca","tid":999650,"uid":144529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T02:13:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}